What is Bitcoin 
1. Bitcoin        = Bitcoin is a digital currency which is used to send and recive money across the world in a decentralized manner with minium transfer fee.

- very very less what compare to bank charges.
- it doesn't involve a third party(no intermidiator)they reducing cost of transactions.
- fast and cheap transfer possible.
- personal identity/information of a user is hidden
- all transaction are cryptographically secure


Bitcoin Kya Hai?
Bitcoin ek Digital Currency hai. Ye koi physical sikka ya note nahi hai jise aap jeb mein rakh sakein. Ye puri tarah se internet par chalti hai. Isse aap online chizein kharid sakte hain ya invest kar sakte hain. Bitcoin ko chalane ke liye kisi bank ki zaroorat nahi hoti; iska saara hisab-kitab wahi Blockchain rakhti hai.

Bitcoin ek digital currency hai jo blockchain technology use karti hai:

Jaise rupee, dollar - waise digital paisa
Koi bank ya sarkar control nahi karti
Internet pe directly person-to-person transfer
Limited supply hai - sirf 21 million bitcoin ban sakte hain